{"tid":832274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［長文］ 入黎開解一下我","createTime":"2018-09-22T15:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T01:35:02.000Z","uid":202429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6019f236bfb82a1bd7a18f7480fec6b22d9da00a","tid":832274,"uid":202429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:57:01.000Z","msg":"依家只好自己一個訓喺張床度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  小妹只細同屋企人嘅關係一向唔係太好，記得細細個時候唔記得做錯啲咩被佢用部單車飛落我度，跟著係咁用腳踩到我流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n由細到大，佢仲未試過去了解我，每一次考試衰咗、比人記欠交功課就老母前老母後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢成日睇低我，無論我做啲咩佢都一定會睇死我，話我一定衰鳩硬點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n直到今日，佢放工一番黎見到我阿哥未做曬功課就打機就即刻拍曬抬開片，我阿哥係一啲比較內向嘅男仔所以就係咁比佢捱屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁啱我同婆婆出完街番黎佢就順便屌鳩埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌我做咩唔聽佢電話，咁我部垃圾二手機個震機功能係壞鳩柒咗，搭車番黎個時啲人又鬼殺咁嘈，撚知道有人打黎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好好聲同佢解釋佢就左耳入右耳出，我真係忍唔撚住咪粗聲粗氣解釋，點知佢即刻起曬鋼咁想同我隻揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我咁多年黎忍屎忍尿日日比佢日日當狗撚嘅怨氣一下之間就比佢個閪樣迫撚出黎，跟著我咪MMA抱起佢對腳然後同佢攬炒飛落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條老野即刻起身用腳踩我，跟住咪MMA佢多一次囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個一刻真係心有火，成撚日都話我咁有本事咪自己搬出去住，自己交學費囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  講撚到生我出黎為我供書教學好似好撚偉大咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時就唔理鳩人，放工番黎都唔會主動同自己仔女傾計，靜係識對住部電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次番屋企叫一叫大家之後就唔撚會理大家 <br />\n<br />\n都係個句，唔識教仔唔識點同子女溝通真係唔好生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4adcac70910088ea35cd9a5ea3a4221761fe191d","tid":832274,"uid":202429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353f6c8116628d378c5af28ccc712ba92a3d265b","tid":832274,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:59:36.000Z","msg":"新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果唔係就扮順佢意<br />\n之後起飛腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5db1cf45333a473db34bdc7a3720af90b5650d9","tid":832274,"uid":202429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"353f6c8116628d378c5af28ccc712ba92a3d265b","tid":832274,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:59:36.000Z","msg":"新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果唔係就扮順佢意<br />\n之後起飛腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時都唔知自己係啱定錯"},{"pid":"ccb6c3cce10f9d8a86bd76a47e312d2c85d27a2b","tid":832274,"uid":4085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"我同你情況差唔多 好明白 對上個星期佢都叫我咁叻就走 唔好係到住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45864dd8c6029d355ad97c77b845284c788ee06e","tid":832274,"uid":202429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ccb6c3cce10f9d8a86bd76a47e312d2c85d27a2b",